    "nom_orig": "???",
    "texte_orig": "Ciaaaao,[SP]Ma-ya![SP]What's[SP]with[SP]the[SP]high[SP]school\nentourage?[SP]They[SP]don't[SP]look[SP]like[SP]they're[SP]here\nto[SP]box.",
